dialogues.name: Vicent
dialogues.content: Good morning! How have you been familiarising yourself with the school all this time? Are you keeping up with your studies?

dialogues.name: Yvonne
dialogues.content: Thank you, Vincent! I've been doing well recently!

dialogues.name: Yvonne
dialogues.content: I have some questions here that are confusing me, but since math is your strong suit, can you help me out?

dialogues.name: Vincent
dialogues.content: Of course, it would be great if I can help you! We can go to the library.
